text.tspan: I look for an online platform that delivers live match statistics
4. Up to date with the match data.
I'm a working software professional and a tennis enthusiast. I
always love to follow up on all the major tennis tournaments
and watch matches at the venue. Due to full-time work in my
new organization, I was not able to make any plans. so I would
like to look for an application that serves all the data and
insights about the live and past matches on the tournament.
1. To view a glimpse of the game and set.
2. To view the detailed match statistics.
3. To see the ball trajectory and its impact on the court.
4. To know more about the strokes and rallies.
5. To compare the previous results between the players.
1. Lack of information on what exactly the features do.
2. Unclear of how to extract the needed data.
3. Hard to perceive data when missing assistive labels.
4. Difficult to relate the points with the match.
